                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Slight chance of a light shower. Winds south to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="1" start-time-local="2026-05-09T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-05-10T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-05-08T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-05-09T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Medium chance of showers, most likely in the morning. Light winds becoming southerly 15 to 20 km/h in the early afternoon then becoming light in the late afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to around 10 with daytime temperatures reaching around 18.</text>
