            <forecast-period index="3" start-time-local="2026-05-11T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-05-12T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-05-10T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-05-11T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Slight chance of a shower in the south, near zero chance elsewhere. Light winds. Overnight temperatures falling to between 5 and 8 with daytime temperatures reaching around 19.</text>
